title: Production of new motor vehicles in Canada 2016
summary: The Production of new motor in Canada is fluctuating all the time in 2016 .
Overall , it drops for nearly a half in the first Month , and oscillated till July .
Then , it rises to a bit higher than the Production in January till November and December .
gold: The diagram showes the Production of new motor vehicles in Dollar over the year 2016 in Canada . In januarry less than 4500000 vehicles were produced ( lowest ) . Till April the production increase steadyly and reach the highest value .
